PrecisOrder varying Order No. 1991-R-40 of the National Transportation Agency, which the Agency Order authorized the Rural Municipality of Canaan and the Village of Lucky Lake together with CN to proceed with the construction of a crossing, by deleting the clauses authorizing construction of the crossing and assigning costs of maintenance and of construction to the municipalities and by replacing them with clauses ordering the closure of the crossing.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1993-0101 Publication Date: 1993-03-10
Attachments
precis:
Order varying Order No. 1991-R-40 of the National Transportation Agency,
which the Agency Order authorized the Rural Municipality of Canaan and the
Village of Lucky Lake together with CN to proceed with the construction of
a crossing, by deleting the clauses authorizing construction of the
crossing and assigning costs of maintenance and of construction to the
municipalities and by replacing them with clauses ordering the closure of
the crossing.
